brand: Necktar of the World as Ending
message: Wild growth outside the walled gardens
description:
"The piece must imperatively correspond to a reason for humanity to continue or to stop."

Shall we continue or stop?

notes.artist: A mere journey through time, the great work of anachronistic alchemists... Difficult to define Necktar 2017, till the first cycle is not achieved. Currently it was? a compilation of hors norme (not normal) music for free sharing, articulated in several thematic episodes. For know what it will be ultimately, unless we can travel through time, it won't be until 2017.
notes.caption: REAL / Perception / REALITY = ILLUSION
